    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything is nearly ready, boil a kettle</p><p>Combine your <strong>gravy paste </strong>with 125ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[190ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, whisk thoroughly</p><p>Put it in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 30-40 secs or until thickened and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>gravy</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>bacon-wrapped roast chicken </strong>on a clean board</p>",
